---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="关于" description="关于这个博客" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <section class="card prose">
        <h1>关于我</h1>
        <p>你好，我是白小，这里记录日常折腾与技术笔记。</p>
        <p>主题方向：OpenWrt、网络代理、开发效率、实用工具。</p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
